{"tid":1321144,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"減肥究竟係要重訓多定Cardio多？","createTime":"2019-07-15T14:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T02:04:12.000Z","uid":229862,"like":5,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf43c1d9affc5a245dfeb290f450bb6cedb3c2a","tid":1321144,"uid":229862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:54:44.000Z","msg":"16xcm 68kg<br />\n之前試過跑步，跑咗三個月，每星期一次，但係冇乜效，好似仲重咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽人講話重訓都有用，但重訓會唔會練到好大隻？"},{"pid":"57fd5ca5654bebeecece864102ab3a8226670fc3","tid":1321144,"uid":22488,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:58:25.000Z","msg":"你估做幾下掌上壓就真係the rock咁樣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要兩樣做齊先最有效<br />\nCardio係燒脂<br />\n重訓練肌肉"},{"pid":"3db0010aecd1c060402bddcdbe2858bd6e4b948e","tid":1321144,"uid":120727,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"quote":{"pid":"eaf43c1d9affc5a245dfeb290f450bb6cedb3c2a","tid":1321144,"uid":229862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:54:44.000Z","msg":"16xcm 68kg<br />\n之前試過跑步，跑咗三個月，每星期一次，但係冇乜效，好似仲重咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽人講話重訓都有用，但重訓會唔會練到好大隻？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"每星期一次？ 你自己覺得會唔會有效？"},{"pid":"b1ec8eb6a6be0d63f9dd1dff556eabe00eecf04a","tid":1321144,"uid":56453,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:59:04.000Z","msg":"會啊<br />\n好容易就會練到大舊衰咁<br />\n減肥唔洗重訓"},{"pid":"22c66973a1c653e9f585ecc77bc3e5529d1611f5","tid":1321144,"uid":81256,"like":11,"dislike":10,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T14:59:21.000Z","msg":"重訓為主<br />\n帶氧做輔助<br />\n<br />\n其實體重加減，王道係計卡路里<br />\n卡路里消耗 &gt; 吸引 = 減重<br />\n<br />\n千期唔好信咩唔食殿粉質<br />\n想知再慢慢講<br />\n利申：體適能教練牌，自己減左10幾磅"},{"pid":"f38beefa1a0b210ce273c132563dc2a66cd83ef2","tid":1321144,"uid":128472,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:00:07.000